items.name: Star Wars Games
items.title: Star Wars Games
items.headline: The force is strong at the Star Wars Game Wikia
items.desc: The Star Wars Games Wikia is a Wikia community dedicated to being the number one resource of everything related to Star War Games. These games include the popular Battlefront series, as well as the Knights of the Old Republic. Our community covers all the information related to the characters, the weapons, the stories, the levels, and whatever else is found within these games. Anybody is free to join and help make this Wikia a better resource.

items.name: Tony Hawk's Games Wiki
items.title: Tony Hawk's Games Wiki
items.headline: Tony Hawk's Games Wiki
items.desc:
On this wiki you can find info about any Tony Hawk's game released in the series. Find all of the secrets you didn't know, solve the mysteries of your childhood or add the additional info you know about it.  You're welcome!

This wiki covers following games:

Main Series

    Tony Hawk's Pro Skater
    Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 2
    Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 3
    Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 4
    Tony Hawk's Underground
    Tony Hawk's Underground 2
    Tony Hawk's American Wasteland
    Tony Hawk's Project 8
    Tony Hawk's Proving Ground
    Tony Hawk: Ride
    Tony Hawk: Shred 

Spin-offs:

    Tony Hawk's American Sk8land
    Tony Hawk's Downhill Jam
    Tony Hawk's Motion 

Others:

    Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 2X
    Tony Hawk's Underground 2 Remix
    Tony Hawk's Pro Skater HD

items.name: Game Shows Wiki
items.title: Game Shows Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to U.S. Game Shows Wiki
items.desc: Welcome one and all to the U.S. Game Shows Wiki, the wiki about United States game shows that anyone can edit. Our ever growing community consists of fans of various game shows in the United States. From old to new we have it all. We are glad to have you as part of our community and we hope you enjoy our content!

items.title: Humongous Entertainment Games Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Humongous Entertainment Wiki!
items.desc:
The Humongous Entertainment Wiki is an encyclopedia about the many fun games made by Humongous Entertainment. Humongous Entertainment Inc. is an American video game developer. The company is known for its line of educational games for children.

They developed original characters such as Freddi Fish, Pajama Sam, and Spy Fox.

items.name: Yume Nikki Fangames Wiki
items.title: Yume Nikki Fangames Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Yume Nikki Fangames Wiki!
items.desc: Yume Nikki is an experimental Japanese indie game from 2005 by developer Kikiyama created on Enterbrain's RPG Maker 2003. It's original elements of gameplay have inspired a large cult following and a wide variety of fangames and spiritual successors. This wiki strives to document these games as well as provide something of a walkthrough for them.
